妮可·舒金格 (Nicole Scherzinger) 表示拉塞尔·布兰德 (Russell Brand) 帽子评论与“政治无关” https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicole-scherzinger-says-russell-brand-hat-c​​omment-not-politically-lated-3811201?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nicole-scherzinger-says-russell-品牌帽子评论与政治无关Daniel PetersSat, 09 Nov 2024 10:28:53 +0000 Music NewsNewsDonald Trump https://www.nme.com/?p=3811201 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="妮可·斯彻金格" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> “这顶帽子哪里可以买到！？”舒金格对拉塞尔·布兰德庆祝特朗普获胜的帖子发表了评论，然后删除了她的回复</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicole-scherzinger-says-russell-brand-hat-comment-not-politically-related-3811201">妮可·舒金格 (Nicole Scherzinger) 表示拉塞尔·布兰德 (Russell Brand) 帽子评论与“政治无关”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="妮可·斯彻金格" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/NicoleScherzinger-2024-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicole-scherzinger">妮可·斯彻金格 (Nicole Scherzinger)</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicole-scherzinger-comes-under-fire-for-response-to-russell-brand-celebrating-trumps-win-3810930">评论拉塞尔·布兰德 (Russell Brand) 庆祝特朗普获胜的帖子</a>后回应了批评，称这与“政治无关”。</p><p>本周早些时候，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pussycat-dolls">小野猫</a>歌手对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/russell-brand">布兰德</a>Instagram 上的一张照片做出了回应，照片中他举着一顶红色帽子，上面写着：“再次让耶稣成为第一。”</p><p> “这顶帽子哪里可以买到！？”谢尔金格在评论部分写道，然后删除了她的回复。</p><p>这让许多人相信她透露自己是特朗普的粉丝，因为这顶帽子与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/donald-trump/">特朗普的</a>MAGA 帽子相似，上面印有特朗普的口号：“让美国再次伟大”。</p><p>这在网上引起了强烈反对，许多人对她对特朗普的明显支持感到愤怒，而且在第四频道的<i>快讯</i>节目、 <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/uk/crime/article/russell-brand-detectives-ask-prosecutors-consider-bringing-charges-q7w9cnvf6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《泰晤士报》</i></a>和<i>《星期日泰晤士报》</i>联合调查后，布兰德最近被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/russell-brand-accused-of-rape-sexual-assault-and-emotional-abuse-3498938">指控犯有多项性犯罪</a>行为。</p><p>布兰德强烈否认所有指控，称他所有的性关系“绝对都是双方自愿的”。</p><p>在昨天（11 月 8 日）分享的<a href="https://www.instagram.com/nicolescherzinger/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram 故事</a>中，她对这种强烈反对做出了回应：“我对最近因一些社交媒体帖子造成的伤害深表歉意。当我对这些帖子发表评论时，我犯了一个错误，没有意识到它们很容易被解读为与政治相关，我向任何可以理解地得出这一结论的人道歉。” </p><figure id="attachment_3137393" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3137393" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3137393" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Nicole-Scherzinger_2021-.jpg" alt="妮可·斯彻金格" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Nicole-Scherzinger_2021-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Nicole-Scherzinger_2021--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Nicole-Scherzinger_2021--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Nicole-Scherzinger_2021--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Nicole-Scherzinger_2021--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Nicole-Scherzinger_2021--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3137393" class="wp-caption-text">妮可·斯彻金格。图片来源：Cedric Ribeiro/Getty Images for the Global Citizen Forum</figcaption></figure><p> “人们做出了许多假设，这些假设并不能反映我是谁、我代表什么、或者我投票给谁，”她继续说道。 “许多因总统选举结果而感到受伤和担忧的边缘化社区是我最关心的人。在我的一生和职业生涯中，我一如既往地与他们站在一起。如果你认识我，你就知道这一点。”</p><p>然后她解释了她的帖子互动：“我相信我参与的帖子是为了鼓励人们选择爱和信仰——“把耶稣放在第一位。”对我来说，基督体现了和平、同情、希望，最重要的是无条件的爱，特别是对于那些现在最没有感受到这种爱的人。”</p><p> “我来自一个充满爱的地方，我将永远支持使我们更加紧密的价值观。我们现在怀着同情心走到一起，比以往任何时候都更加相爱，这一点非常重要。”</p><p>在其他地方，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">麦当娜</a>在内的许多艺术家对特朗普再次当选美国总统表示失望， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-on-trumps-election-win-a-convicted-felon-rapist-bigot-was-chosen-3810754">麦当娜写道</a>：“试图让我理解为什么一个<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-as-donald-trump-found-guilty-on-all-34-counts-in-hush-money-case-3761096">被定罪的重罪犯</a>、强奸犯、偏执狂被选来领导我们的国家，因为他对经济有好处吗？” </p><figure id="attachment_3810133" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3810133" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3810133" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Donald-Trump-2024.jpg" alt="唐纳德·特朗普，GTA 6" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Donald-Trump-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Donald-Trump-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Donald-Trump-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Donald-Trump-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Donald-Trump-2024-1392x884.jpg